<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說很快地，<delay8 />這座島上就要舉辦
第一場大型活動了呢。<delay20 />
你知道這件事嗎？<delay8 />島上傳得沸沸揚揚唷。<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />我非常期待喔！<delay frames="40" />
希望大家能夠一起熱情參與，<delay8 />
讓活動順利進行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />終於快到了，<delay8 />
明天<tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay8 />
要第一次舉辦大活動呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也要盡力參加，<delay8 />
好好炒熱活動的氣氛～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個星期六要舉辦釣魚大會喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想你一定<delay20 />也會參加的對吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />釣魚既不需要跑步，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也不會流汗，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太適合我了呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是釣魚大會囉。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你都準備好了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我從昨天<delay20 />就已經準備好<delay8 />
必要的用具了。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />話雖這麼說，<delay20 />
其實也只需要一支釣竿而已呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個星期六要舉辦捕蟲大會喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然<delay8 />我不太擅長捕蟲，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我還是會盡力加油的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是捕蟲大會了喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是不是也該照自己的步調，<delay8 />
好好努力一下呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我跟你說，<delay8 />明天就是<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />期待已久的煙火大會囉！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟是難得的活動，<delay8 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我們好好打扮後，一起享受吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經<delay8 />都準備好了嗎？<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快樂家協會的
評分結果就會出爐囉。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看是要打掃房間還是重新布置<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想做最後的掙扎<delay8 />
就趕緊趁現在吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
快樂家協會發出的評價，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看過了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />住家的評價也是反映出自己的一面鏡子。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我也覺得<delay8 />
應該要好好接受指教<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年也平安度過了。<10_4 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺<delay8 />一年真的過得好快呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但這也是自己在這一年過得很開心的證明吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好～<delay20 />當作今年的收尾，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在今年最後一天晚上，<delay8 />就和大家一起
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到廣場上參加跨年倒數吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">一想到明天<tag a="90" b="27" />年就要結束了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還是很讓人不敢置信呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不如去參加跨年倒數活動，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為今年劃下完美的句點，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後清爽地迎接新年好了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />馬上就要5月了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />也就是說……<delay20 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快到勞動節了耶！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />勞動節活動會在別的島上舉辦對吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />好期待5月1日喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">今天是4月30日<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />明天不就是勞動節了嗎！？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果沒有<colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" />給的<colour id="1" />勞動節旅行券<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
就沒辦法去活動會場了。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天必須得去一趟<colour id="1" />服務處<colour id="65535" />才行，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你記得<delay20 />10月31日是什麼日子嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯，<delay20 />就是萬聖節喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想島上的大家<delay8 />
都想在當天拿到你的糖果，<delay20 />
你趁現在準備好<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會比較好喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦，<delay20 />你問沒有準備會怎麼樣？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這麼好奇的話，要親身體驗一下嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從失敗裡學習<delay8 />也是人生的一部分喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天終於就是萬聖節了呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />我很用心準備了裝扮，<delay8 />
你要好好期待萬聖節當天喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay20 />你準備好
萬聖節<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />需要的糖果了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也很希望能從你手上<delay8 />拿到那東西，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />記得要準備我的份喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我問你，<delay8 />你知道嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感恩節就快到了喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這座島上很難得能見到一流主廚，<delay8 />
所以我非常期待那一天到來喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過既然是難得的慶典，<delay8 />我是不是
也該親自下廚做點料理呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的！<delay frames="40" />我好期待喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你有辦法參加<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天的感恩節嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我當然是一定會參加囉！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當天我不是待在廣場就是待在家裡，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是我們能相遇就好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等一下，<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay frames="30" />
平安夜就快到了喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到平安夜就會想到交換禮物吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我<delay8 />正在想<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要送什麼禮物給你，<delay frames="40" />
所以你也要準備好<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送給我的禮物喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">明天就是平安夜了喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你準備好要交換的禮物了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可要好好地包裝喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我找到了<delay8 />一樣很不錯的禮物，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你敬請期待囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>